&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Negotiate&lt;/strong&gt;: Engage and secure high ROI marketing partnerships across travel, hospitality, universities, and entertainment venues to establish brand awareness, product adoption, and top notch customer experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create&lt;/strong&gt;: Bring to life partnerships in creative ways that align Waymo’s business needs with partner audience passion points. Build out multi-channel marketing plans based on mutual audience and brand voice principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build Relationships&lt;/strong&gt;: Represent Waymo as the key point of contact for a portfolio of partners, maximizing relationships with the partners’ extended network of affiliates and thought leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measure Impact&lt;/strong&gt;: Ensure all partnerships drive measurable and ongoing impact by providing consistent KPI reporting to guide future partnership strategies and decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in partner marketing, high-stakes negotiation, and large-scale activations in-house or in an agency environment for B2C brands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record leading complex business negotiations with positive results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience bringing to life multi-channel marketing partnerships and consumer promotions with significant brand and operational impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compelling verbal and written communication skills with standout strength building rapport, advocating for the business, and tailoring approaches to the audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dynamic, big picture strategic thinking coupled with detail-oriented, hands-on execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working at or directly with the hospitality, travel, education, and/or large scale venue partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity and experience with the autonomous vehicle, automotive, or high-growth technology industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience collaborating deeply with product and technical teams, ensuring all marketing initiatives are grounded in the reality of the technology and product capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of brand safety and policy issues related to emerging technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
