&lt;li&gt;Act as the &quot;go-to&quot; subject matter expert, instrumental in developing and improving business intelligence infrastructure. Use this deep technical knowledge to inform team strategy and influence broader best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish a wide network across the company, leveraging it to source new opportunities for the team and contributing to project prioritization by internalizing where resources (both yours and team) are most impactful&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop project roadmaps, establish long-term project goals, and serve as a consistent role model who models and supports others in using the Waymo Way behaviors, especially when addressing technical and organizational challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coding skills (SQL)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least &lt;strong&gt;8+&lt;/strong&gt; years of relevant experience, and &lt;strong&gt;2+&lt;/strong&gt; years of proven ability to manage people&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to influence decision making through data storytelling and visualization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Stakeholder Education &amp;amp; Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in the AV industry / Mapping / Ridesharing / Consumer Tech / Supply chain / Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a dynamic environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates initiative and foresight in identifying and addressing business needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The expected base salary range for this full-time position across US locations is listed below. Actual starting pay will be based on job-related factors, including exact work location, experience, relevant training and education, and skill level. Your recruiter can share more about the specific salary range for the role location or, if the role can be performed remote, the specific salary range for your preferred location, during the hiring process.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
