&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of data structures, algorithms, and software design principles. Demonstrated ability to debug and solve technical problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in at least one programming language (C++, Java, or Python).&lt;/li&gt;
