&lt;li&gt;Own the complete model development lifecycle, from data mining and processing to model training, evaluation, validation, and productionization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with partner ML teams, such as Waymo Perception and Waymo AI Foundations, to adapt cutting-edge research into scalable, reliable, and production-grade solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
