&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on experience in Machine Learning, with a strong focus on computer vision and/or deep learning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in at least one major deep learning framework (e.g., TensorFlow, PyTorch, JAX).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience owning problems end-to-end and working across various parts of the systems stack to deliver results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B.S. in Computer Science, a similar technical field, or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
