&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with foundation models and techniques for model adaptation (e.g., few-shot learning, transfer learning, domain adaptation).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of publications in top-tier ML/CV conferences (e.g., NeurIPS, ICML, CVPR, ICCV, ECCV).&lt;/li&gt;
