&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS or MS in Mechanical Engineering, Industrial Engineering, or a related technical field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of manufacturing engineering or planning experience specifically within the automotive or transportation sector.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven hands-on experience in manufacturing process development and project management, with a track record of taking content from prototype to production.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of DFA/DFM methodologies and manufacturing standard creation used to directly influence and optimize product designs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience managing New Product Introductions (NPI), technical documentation, and complex product lifecycles in coordination with supply chain techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in collaborating and working cross functionally with development, operations, supply chain, contract manufacturers and system engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fluency in technical Japanese&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We prefer:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
