&lt;li&gt;Conduct initial and recurring BCP readiness tests and exercises, identifying and resolving gaps to ensure continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize a data-driven approach to Enterprise Resilience, with the ability to provide the Executive Leadership Team with clear, actionable insights into enterprise-wide resilience risk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
