&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of risk assessment methodologies, business impact analysis (BIA), and the development of effective resilience strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in developing and implementing actionable Business Continuity Plans (BCPs) and conducting readiness tests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with policy development and adherence to established document management standards.&lt;/li&gt;
