&lt;li&gt;Set up and sustain mechanisms that enable organizational efficiencies, and improve speed of decision making and execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate across all levels of the organization to ensure all partners are aware of program decisions, status, and changes&lt;/li&gt;
