&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in engineering&amp;nbsp; program management, with at least 3+ years focused specifically on data-centric programs for machine learning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of the ML model life-cycle and the critical role of data within it (e.g., data sourcing, labeling, quality evaluation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to manage complex technical programs, including structuring project plans, identifying dependencies, and driving execution using Agile methodologies (e.g., Scrum)&lt;/li&gt;
