&lt;li&gt;Requirements Gathering: Formalize demand forecasts into detailed real estate requirement documents for expansion, consolidation, and sequencing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Predictive Modeling: Build and maintain supply/demand models to generate the data-driven forecasts used for long-term strategic planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inform Documentation: Produce standardized reports and strategic briefings that translate complex analytics into actionable insights for leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Liaison: Define and document technical requirements for the analytics team to ensure dashboards align with business strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical Support: Execute data-heavy ad-hoc analysis to support business case development and multi-market occupier engagements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
