&lt;li&gt;Experience: 4 years of experience in data analysis, corporate real estate, or business intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Writing: Proven ability to create clear, concise documentation and process workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical Rigor: Exceptional attention to detail with the ability to manage large datasets without compromising accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
