&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in delivering successful ASIL D certified products to market, including full safety case ownership from concept to production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience leading and performing complex safety analyses (HARA, FMEA, FTA, etc.) for autonomous or highly complex E/E systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive knowledge of advanced safety standards beyond ISO 26262 that can be applied to AI components within autonomous systems (such as ISO 21448, SOTIF), as well as relevant quality/reliability standards and international regulatory requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
