&lt;p&gt;A strong desire to build tools for enterprise users to streamline and simplify processes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Passion for autonomous vehicle technology and making complex data accessible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
