&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Product Management, Engineering (Mechanical, Electrical), UX Research, and Operations teams to translate complex user needs and technical requirements into tangible, user-centric hardware and experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Develop and communicate production-intent design concepts through a high-fidelity process, including 2D sketching, 3D CAD modeling, and creating both digital and physical prototypes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams and external vendors to oversee the transition from design to manufacturing, ensuring design intent, quality, and CMF (Color, Materials, Finish) are maintained in the final product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define and champion the physical product and hardware strategy, ensuring it aligns with the overall Waymo brand and user experience goals&lt;/li&gt;
