&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing for complex hardware systems, robotics, or products with a high degree of technical integration&lt;/li&gt;
