&lt;li&gt;Develop a data flywheel approach to automatically scale sensor validation approaches&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with in-house hardware and perception teams on novel sensing modalities and next-generation perception solutions&lt;/li&gt;
