&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated technical ownership of electromechanical motion control systems (e.g., Steer-by-Wire, Electronic Braking, Flight Controls)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in Python for data analysis, scripting, or tool development (must be able to write scripts to process logs/data). Ability to read and understand C++&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with requirements management traceability (e.g., DOORS, Jama) and interface control documents (ICDs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Computer Science, Robotics, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
