&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Understand low-level differences in computation outputs, e.g., due to hardware differences, compiler changes, or large-scale cloud issues and their impact on evaluation vs. onroad behavior&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Automate measurement, develop metrics, and debugging tooling for computational stability across simulation and onboard platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Collaborate across Waymo to streamline integrity workflows, ensuring business-critical operations run smoothly and safely at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;BS/MS in Comp Sci, EE, Robotics, Physics, Math, or related field (or equivalent experience).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Experience in C++ or Python, building scalable pipelines and tooling.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
