&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work closely with onboard and research engineers to scale simulation and enable critical Waymo milestones&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support development, testing and evolution of mapping data in the simulator&lt;/p&gt;
