&lt;li&gt;Build systems that systematically optimize multiple objectives under resource constraints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other engineers, data scientists, statisticians and the leadership team to deliver evaluation products and help make data driven decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion code health and best practices in a large and complex code base&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
