&lt;li&gt;10+ years of deep, hands-on design experience from working directly within one or more automotive OEM design studios (e.g., Ford, GM, Toyota, VW Group, Rivian, Tesla, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proven track record of leading multiple, complex hardware products from ambiguous early concepts to successful mass production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of defining and successfully executing hardware development programs integrating the industrial design work-stream into a larger development schedule&lt;/li&gt;
