&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in robotics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in low level optimization techniques, frameworks (SIMD/CUDA) and ML performance/frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in large scale evaluation techniques/data science and building performance metrics/tooling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in large scale software re-architecture projects&lt;/li&gt;
