&lt;li&gt;Evaluate the continued effectiveness of implemented mitigations to ensure risk profile have not changed; if safety risk has changed supports the identification of new hazards &amp;amp; mitigations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solve challenging and ambiguous problems with long time horizons, helping teammates navigate &quot;uncharted territory&quot; in safety engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Articulate and influence new safety approaches to stakeholders across Product, Legal, Systems Engineering, and Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor of Science in Electrical/Mechatronics/Aerospace Engineering, Computer Engineering, Computer Science, or related technical fields&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong&lt;strong&gt; technical project management &lt;/strong&gt;skills with the ability to manage multiple parallel projects&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of relevant engineering work experience that includes minimum &lt;strong&gt;7&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; years of System Safety engineering&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
