&lt;li&gt;Proficient in applying Systems Engineering principles&amp;nbsp; including defining&lt;strong&gt; SMART safety mitigations&lt;/strong&gt;/requirements and collaborating on effective &lt;strong&gt;verification and validation methods&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
