&lt;li&gt;Develop deep technical understanding of existing and new depot automation features and drive a robust end-to-end verification and monitoring system to ensure these features meet high efficacy goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop qualification methods to launch new features and depots and provide engineering recommendations to senior stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
