&lt;li&gt;Extend existing depot automation features to new vehicle platforms to ensure feature parity across the diverse Waymo fleet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply your existing technical depth to new areas and learn quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
