&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test planning and experimental design, especially designing for safety and repeatability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data analysis and test scripting/automation experience (C/C++, Python, Matlab/Simulink)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project management. Ability to understand the scope of work, available resources and timeline, and translate it into schedules. Being able to make and communicate trade-offs between program conflicts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication, coordination and collaboration skills. Being able to support the execution of multiple tests activities in parallel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor and/or Master&#39;s degree in a relevant engineering or a related field (including ME, EE, CS, Robotics, Controls, Aerospace, etc.) or equivalent practical experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
