&lt;li&gt;Expert in using wireless testing equipment such as Call Boxes, signaling testers, GNSS Simulator, WLAN Access Points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid knowledge with practical experience in at least one of the wireless technologies&amp;nbsp; (5G NR, LTE, GNSS, BLE, Wi-Fi) and experience with SAR, OTA, Coexistence testing, Interoperability testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written/verbal communication, able to work independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands on scripting experience (Shell, Python, Bash) to automate repetitive tasks in various test methods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
