&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5 years of experience in Safety Management Systems (SMS), Organizational Development, or Corporate Governance within safety-sensitive industries (AV, aviation, nuclear, automotive, or similar).&lt;/li&gt;
