&lt;li&gt;Develop tools and methodologies to improve and automate the triage process, to get fast and accurate performance statistics using an automated system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate new hardware specifications and changes, and assess the impact on the autonomous vehicle performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop simulation tools for new sensor emulation, and simulating autonomous vehicle performance with sensor impairments and injected faults&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support sign-off process for all stages of sensing system development and software releases. Present results at milestone sign-off reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop new methodologies and processes for assessing autonomous vehicle performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
