&lt;li&gt;Develop software systems that accelerate onboard release qualification and improve developer velocity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work across front end and back end technologies, perform&amp;nbsp; SRE duties, and dig into test platform details&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support internal and external customers in test engineering and embedded software development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Think big, and take on ambitious projects that require systems thinking and experimentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree or equivalent practical experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;+3 years of experience in C++&lt;/li&gt;
