&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architect a Testing Continuum:&lt;/strong&gt; Define and drive the technical roadmap for a seamless testing continuum, bridging the gap between virtual simulation and high-fidelity hardware-in-the-loop (HIL) environments and enabling automated orchestration, execution, and analysis across the spectrum of test environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scale HIL Infrastructure:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee the development and scaling of our hardware-in-the-loop test infrastructure, ensuring high-availability, automated deployment of new firmware and software, robust execution of regression suites, and high-fidelity test and integration environments for developers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Champion Software Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the senior software engineering leader for the team, ensuring our automation frameworks are production-grade, maintainable, and aligned with industry-leading software development standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Automated V&amp;amp;V:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the technical strategy for automated verification and validation of new software, firmware, hardware, and platform configurations, enabling continuous verification for complex safety-critical systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage &amp;amp; Mentor:&lt;/strong&gt; Grow and manage a diverse team of Software Engineers, Hardware Engineers, and Systems Test Engineers, fostering a culture of technical rigor, inclusive collaboration, and servant leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner Cross-Functionally:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate closely with Hardware Engineering, Software Simulation, and Program leadership to align on resourcing, technical standards, and mission success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education: &lt;/strong&gt;Must have a BS, MS, or PhD in Computer Science, Robotics or similar technical field of study&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SWE Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Extensive experience as a Technical Lead or Manager in a production software environment (C++ and/or Python)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems Thinking:&lt;/strong&gt; A proven track record of managing complex HW/SW integration projects, ideally in robotics, AVs, or aerospace&lt;/li&gt;
