&lt;li&gt;Expertise using advanced statistical methods in an applied setting; familiarity with ML systems/models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated knowledge of data analysis libraries and packages in Python, R, and/or SQL.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
