&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Program Liaison: &lt;/strong&gt;Act as the primary strategic bridge between the Risk &amp;amp; Insurance and other internal teams such as TPM and PM teams to drive the implementation of complex technology, data, and insurance and claims-related projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems Innovation &amp;amp; Automation:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with claims and actuarial teams to design and deploy custom tooling, data visualization dashboards, and automated operational workflows that enhance team productivity and data-driven decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Infrastructure &amp;amp; Partner Management: &lt;/strong&gt;Oversee the full lifecycle of critical regulatory and operational documentation (e.g., ID Cards, COIs) and lead the end-to-end onboarding and management of external partners, including TPAs and brokers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Stakeholder Engagement: &lt;/strong&gt;Develop and lead a comprehensive communication and engagement strategy for internal and external partners, including the management and the delivery of quarterly insurance insights and newsletters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Showcase &amp;amp; Event Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Direct the end-to-end coordination and project management of high-profile internal and external showcases, including the planning and execution of flagship events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
