&lt;li&gt;Provide leadership in integrating the System Safety Methodology with other methodologies of the Waymo safety framework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
