&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Supplier Alliances:&lt;/strong&gt; Cultivate high-level relationships with key market leaders in the BPO and Engineering Services landscape. You will bridge the gap between Waymo’s internal needs and external market capabilities, establishing deep partnerships that unlock innovation and preferential access to talent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enterprise Operations Category Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the category strategy and transformation roadmap for Waymo’s critical operations, ensuring resilience, scalability, and cost-optimization to support rapid market expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
