&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategy &amp;amp; Roadmap:&lt;/strong&gt; Define the technical strategy and 12+ month roadmap for evaluation frameworks that allow for rapid, safe and smooth hill-climbing &amp;amp; release for Waymo Perception models, accelerating multi-city expansion and keeping alignment with company-wide safety goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execution &amp;amp; Delivery:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee the end-to-end delivery of complex evaluation platforms and data pipelines, removing blockers and ensuring the team meets critical release deadlines and accelerates the evolution of Perception models..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary point of contact for the team, collaborating deeply with ML researchers, simulation &amp;amp; ML infra teams, and safety experts to define &amp;amp; measure what &quot;success&quot; looks like for the Waymo Driver.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Guidance:&lt;/strong&gt; Guide technical decision-making and architectural trade-offs (without necessarily writing the code), ensuring the team builds scalable, maintainable, and reliable systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organizational Health:&lt;/strong&gt; Foster a culture of psychological safety, technical excellence, and inclusivity, while managing team capacity and resource planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engineering Management Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 2+ years of experience directly managing software engineering teams, including performance management, hiring, and retention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Background:&lt;/strong&gt; Previous background as a software engineer or technical lead (5+ years) with a strong understanding of evaluation frameworks and methodologies, scalable data pipelines and performance benchmarks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivery Track Record:&lt;/strong&gt; Proven ability to manage complex technical projects with ambiguous requirements and multiple stakeholders, delivering on time and at quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data-Driven Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience using metrics and data to drive team improvements and measure project success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Thinking:&lt;/strong&gt; Ability to translate high-level business goals (e.g., &quot;Launch in Austin&quot;) into concrete technical roadmaps and team priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
