&lt;li&gt;Management of a team of MLEs focused on model quality improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical leadership to improve planner ML models for both short-term product improvements, as well as long-term experimentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate driving behavior issues from logs and understand the root cause&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve performance of the state of the art ML models in Planner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expand the impact of ML models while preserving interpretability and behavioral guarantees&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide mentorship for junior engineers on the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Masters or PhD degree in Computer Science, Machine Learning or a similar discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Python or C++&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Machine Learning models in production systems, particularly ranking and scoring systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven leadership experience guiding an ML team in meeting company objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AV or Robotics experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of Software Engineering experience in complex systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The expected base salary range for this full-time position across US locations is listed below. Actual starting pay will be based on job-related factors, including exact work location, experience, relevant training and education, and skill level. Your recruiter can share more about the specific salary range for the role location or, if the role can be performed remote, the specific salary range for your preferred location, during the hiring process.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
