&lt;li&gt;1+ year of management experience years with 5+ reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AV or Robotics experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Machine Learning models in production systems&lt;/li&gt;
