&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in C++.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MS in Computer Science, or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years experience in developing low latency, large-scale, user facing distributed systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Domain knowledge across the transportation, mobility, and/or autonomous vehicle industries.&lt;/li&gt;
