&lt;p data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role follows a hybrid work schedule and reports to a Director of Technical Program Management.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
