&lt;li&gt;Standardize recruitment workflows globally while allowing for regional adaptations where necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a subject matter expert on technical talent trends, compensation benchmarks, and competitor movement in our three primary hubs.&lt;/li&gt;
