&lt;li&gt;Ability to &quot;speak engineer&quot;—understanding the difference between backend architectures, ML practices, and frontend frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert-level ability to turn raw hiring data into a compelling narrative for executive leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
